WHAT IS NIX API?

The most advanced and effective up-to-date ANTI-FRAUD/ANTI-PROXY API
solution for webmasters which enables quick and easy access prevention to
unwanted and malicious users who are difficult to block using standard
methods.

You can use this advanced technology to protect your member area, payment
gateway, billing system, forum, and so on.

Listed features and advantages of it's use are too big to be mentioned in
this email.

PS. NIX API for free of charge if you place a backlink on your site.

Live demo and learn more: http://nixapi.com/



